{"tid":2216144,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"普京獲提名諾貝爾和平獎","createTime":"2020-09-24T12:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T09:16:19.000Z","uid":44209,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"382c3384271ebf0c4524c3b7ed11550d905ed95d","tid":2216144,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯作家科姆科夫（Sergei Komkov）9月24日表示，他已向挪威諾貝爾委員會提名俄羅斯總統普京（Vladimir Putin）為2021年諾貝爾和平獎的候選人。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯衛星網9月24日報道，科姆科夫24日早些時候在新聞發布會上表示，他已於9月初向挪威諾貝爾委員會遞交提議，提名普京獲得2021年諾貝爾和平獎。「它（提議）是在9月9日寄出的，9月10日，位於奧斯陸的諾貝爾委員會總部收到了它。」 科姆科夫說。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統新聞秘書佩斯科夫（Dmitry Peskov）9月24日當天也被記者問及普京獲諾貝爾和平獎提名一事，俄羅斯衛星通訊社報道，佩斯科夫表示，總統如果被提名將是非常好的事情，如果沒提名也沒甚麼關係。<br />\n<br />\n「考慮被提名者是有一定程序的。如果做出了這樣的決定，那將是偉大的，如果沒有作出這樣的決定，那也不會是一個問題。」佩斯科夫說。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMLTdEQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMLTdEQ.png&h=25c088f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1818f338c6fe6ae80950d5c93223675af45eead5","tid":2216144,"uid":245849,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"和平即獨裁"},{"pid":"62848cb2438dc517d0d54fcd8eccd93c6002ad00","tid":2216144,"uid":44209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1818f338c6fe6ae80950d5c93223675af45eead5","tid":2216144,"uid":245849,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"和平即獨裁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"雜總：幾時有人提名我？"},{"pid":"83ecb031189c41d5e0bfa1aa2839cdf8ecbbf769","tid":2216144,"uid":54975,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"同黑警一齊拎雙冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse